  "detailed_description": "Saving Simon our first project and first game about ''Simon Riley''.<br />\r\nSimon Riley has some puberty problems.He doesn't trust anyone because of family problems.<br />\r\nHe's trying to escape his problems.He sees suicide as an option.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThis game made with RPG Maker.But there isn't any enemy or any action.<br />\r\nWhen playing,<br />\r\n-You will make some choices.This choices're very important for ''Saving'' Simon.<br />\r\n-Simon will tell his story slowly.<br />\r\n-There are a few puzzle maps in this game.",
  "about_the_game": "Saving Simon our first project and first game about ''Simon Riley''.<br />\r\nSimon Riley has some puberty problems.He doesn't trust anyone because of family problems.<br />\r\nHe's trying to escape his problems.He sees suicide as an option.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThis game made with RPG Maker.But there isn't any enemy or any action.<br />\r\nWhen playing,<br />\r\n-You will make some choices.This choices're very important for ''Saving'' Simon.<br />\r\n-Simon will tell his story slowly.<br />\r\n-There are a few puzzle maps in this game.",
